wp-content/uploads/2016/04/wallpaper-1bae1.jpg";s:6:"height";i:1080;s:5:"width";i:1920;}s:27:"parallax_one_our_story_text";s:1476:"<strong>Zyena System</strong> - Website Designing company offers advanced Web Site Designing, Web Hosting, Web Development and Software Development, which enables your business to get access to the Internet Marketing Industry and Website Designing Industry. Get compatible Web Site design as well and search engine optimization for your online business with for your online business with Zyena System.\n<br /><p>\nAt <strong>Zyena System</strong>, we believe in growing along with people, be it our employees or clients. Because it is when they grow the long-term growth and stability of a company is ensured. We believe that growth oriented business happens when people come together and work towards a common goal with sheer focus and commitment. Zyena System is dedicated to building a long-term relationship with each client on the foundations of quality and trust.</p>\n<br />\n<strong>Our Vision:</strong><br />\nTo be one of the most trusted and respected, visionary web development company providing state of the art technological solutions for our clients thereby improving and sustaining a healthy and mutually beneficial business relationship!\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Our Mission:</strong><br />\nTo commit ourselves in taking leadership both in Development and Technology, delivering maximum value to our customers worldwide through our exemplary works, to create a better tomorrow than today and inspire our employees to be the best they can provide to the IT Fraternity!";s:27:"paralax_one_our_story_image";s:64:"http://localhost/WPzyena/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/about-us.jpg";s:36:"paralax_one_services_pinterest_style";s:1:"1";s:34:"parallax_one_our_services_subtitle";s:0:"";s:22:"parallax_one_copyright";s:0:"";s:29:"paralax_one_ribbon_background";s:0:"";s:25:"parallax_one_ribbon_title";s:0:"";s:24:"parallax_one_button_text";s:0:"";s:24:"parallax